get.description:
Get user's account 2FA configuration. Configuration contains configs for different 2FA providers.

Example:
```
{
  "configs": {
    "EMAIL": {
      "providerType": "EMAIL",
      "useByDefault": true,
      "email": "tenant@itona.ai"
    },
    "TOTP": {
      "providerType": "TOTP",
      "useByDefault": false,
      "authUrl": "otpauth://totp/TB%202FA:tenant@itona.ai?issuer=TB+2FA&secret=PLACEHOLDER_SECRET"
    },
    "SMS": {
      "providerType": "SMS",
      "useByDefault": false,
      "phoneNumber": "+380501253652"
    }
  }
}
```

Available for any authorized user.

